subject: Rajasthan History
question_en: Which royal family ruled over Amer Fort?
question_hi: अमेर के मुख्य मात्राओं का कौन सा बनाया गया था?
explanation_en:
Amer Fort was built by the Kachwaha dynasty, but it was ruled by Tikam Singh, a member of the Kachwaha family during its later years.
